subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description: The project's main objectives are to: develop analytical tools, including a  more functional donor assistance database (CDAD); enhance the capacities of government professionals for strategic planning and reporting;  create a network of highly professional and trained employees with expertise in aid coordination  and improve the established practice of regular donor meetings.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Aid Coordination, phase III
